reviews.text: Very delicious Coconut Tart and Chicken Pie.
average food; a bit overpriced; quite crowded
very local hong kong style cafe..restaurant with decent quality local food. worth a try

I tasted Apple Pie, Chicken Pie and Shrimp Toast. Chicken pie is normal but the shrimp toast and apple pie are excellent. Shrimp toast is very crispy but the taste of the shrimp is very fresh still. Apple pie is not made with cinnamon and the apple taste is very explicit.

Piping hot fry and clay pot dishes. Great service and authentic flavour. The staff were going that extra mile to put everyone in booths. They checked in to make sure we got extra soup and dessert. All in all wonderful experience.

reviews.text: 蘋果批配上提子乾想不到又幾好食👍🏻
炸雞肶一流🖒

蘋果批14元x2 、雞批14元x2、蛋球9元x1
店員收左我68元，佢用左個盒裝俾我，我估個盒要3元
蘋果批及雞批的味道一般般普普通通，唔值得專程去食，如果經過買返件都唔錯，反而意外買咗蛋球一個，好好味，質素很好，當日食咗半個，我放落雪櫃第二日再食，依然咁好味。
宵夜之選，半夜三更，乜都有，你想點吖？
貴和質素差。炸雞脾太乾冇味似咬柴，芝士面自己煮好味啲。。
